@Gateway_HostAddress = http://localhost:5005
@AuthService_HostAddress = http://localhost:5165
@Token = paste-admin-jwt-here

### Admin users - list all users through gateway
GET {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/admin/users
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}
Accept: application/json

### Admin users - create SAV user through gateway
POST {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/admin/users
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Test",
  "lastName": "SAV",
  "phoneNumber": "+216 22 000 000",
  "address": "Tunis",
  "email": "test.sav@sav.local",
  "password": "SavTest!123",
  "role": 1,
  "isActive": true
}

### Admin users - update user through gateway, password omitted to keep current password
PUT {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/admin/users/1
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Test",
  "lastName": "SAV Updated",
  "phoneNumber": "+216 22 000 001",
  "address": "Tunis",
  "email": "test.sav@sav.local",
  "role": 1,
  "isActive": true
}

### Admin users - delete user through gateway
DELETE {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/admin/users/1
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}
